{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/Logo_fr.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a series of unfortunate events, you find yourself surrounded by an ice-covered wilderness. Isolated from the rest of the world, you must rely on your own wists and limited resources to survive these harsh conditions in this\u00a0<strong>Multiplayer Sandbox  Survival in VR</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/Headline1new.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main goal is to stay alive, but how?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build your Base</strong>: Construct a shelter to escape the frost, warm up, protect from wild animals, wait out a snowstorm, store resources, and craft needed equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tools &amp; Weapons</strong>: You will require a variety of tools to fully exploit your surroundings. Each tool and weapon has its purpose and durability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hunt, Craft &amp; Gather</strong>: Hunt animals to gain food and resources. Collect items to craft tools, weapons, or clothing necessary for survival. Pay attention to your backpack's limited space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/fr_1.gif?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/cut_4.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/headline_2new.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Surviving isn't easy. Strategizing your moves is crucial to staying alive. Complete essential tasks during daylight and be aware of the darkness, as nighttime brings lower temperatures. Weather conditions are unpredictable and change dynamically, so always be prepared! Remember that not every place is safe; some may be inaccessible based on your current gear. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/fr_2.gif?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/cut_4.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/headline3new.png?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival isn\u2019t just about staying alive, it\u2019s also about staying sane. Your sanity affects how you perceive the world. If you neglect it, reality may start to blur with illusion. Fake sounds and creatures will certainly make survival even more challenging. But beware - some figments of your imagination can harm you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/fr3.gif?t=1738840690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/cut_4.png?t=1738840690\" />The project is  co-funded by the MEDIA strand of the European Union\u2019s Creative Europe Programme.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054950/extras/eu5.png?t=1738840690\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3054950?t=1738840690","background_raw":"https://store.akamai